info.author: Luke Pinner and Simon Oliver
info.description: MetaGETA is a python application for discovering and extracting metadata from spatial raster datasets (metadata crawler) and transforming it into xml (metadata transformation). A number of generic and specialised imagery formats are supported. The format support has a plugin architecture and more formats can easily be added.
info.name: MetaGETA
info.summary: Metadata Gathering, Extraction and Transformation Application
